        <body>
          <div type="edition">
              <div type="textpart" subtype="incipit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <note>The following incipit is taken from <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/PEN2K2AG"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Grebaut1935Formules"/><title level="a">Deux formules de bénédicité</title><title level="j">Aethiopica</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Sylvain</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Grébaut</t:surname></author><date>1935</date><biblScope unit="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">2</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">49-57</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">52-53</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                  <ab>ሰአልናከ፡ መሐሪ፡ ሰዓልናከ፡ ፈጣሪ፡ ሰዓልናከ፡ ከሀሊ፡ ዘኢትፈልጥ፡ ወኢትሌሊ፨
                    በየማንከ፡ ነቅዓ፡ ሕይወት፡ በየማንከ፡ ነቅዓ፡ በረከት፡ ፈልፈለ፡ ፍሥሐ፡ ወሐሤት፨
                    ባርከነ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ በበረከተ፡ ሰማውያን፡ ወምድራውያን፡ በበረከተ፡ ነቢያት፡ ወሐዋርያት፡ በበረከተ፡ ጻድቃን፡ ወሰማዕት፡
                  </ab>
              </div>
              <div type="textpart" subtype="explicit" xml:lang="gez">
                  <note>The following explicit is taken from <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/PEN2K2AG"><seg type="journalArticle"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:Grebaut1935Formules"/><title level="a">Deux formules de bénédicité</title><title level="j">Aethiopica</title><author><t:forename xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Sylvain</t:forename><t:surname xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0">Grébaut</t:surname></author><date>1935</date><biblScope unit="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope unit="issue">2</biblScope><biblScope unit="page">49-57</biblScope><citedRange unit="page">53</citedRange></bibl>.</note>
                  <ab>ወለእመቦ፡ ተገብረ፡ ውስቴቱ፡ ኅምዝ፡ ወሥራይ፡ ይሰዓር፨
                    ባርክ፡ ለነ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘንተ፡ ኅብስተ፡ ወዘንተ፡ ፅዋዓ።
                      ቀድስ፡ ለነ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ አምላክነ፡ ዘንተ፡ ኅብስተ፡ ወዘንተ፡ ጸዋዓ።
                      ቀድስ፡ ለነ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘንተ፡ ኅብስተ፡ ወዘንተ፡ ጽዋዓ።
                      አምዕዝ፡ ለነ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ዘንተ፡ ኅብስተ፡ ወዘንተ፡ ፅዋዓ፡ እስመ፡ ኵሉ፡ ዘጸውዓ፡ ስመ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ይድኅን፡ ወየሐዩ፡ እምክወሉ፡
                      ኅምዝ፡ ወሥራይ፨ ከማሁ፡ አድኅነነ፡ እምኅምዝ፡ ጸላዒ፡ ወፀር፡ ሊተ፡ ለገብርከ፡ ገብረ፡ ክርስቶስ፡ ገብረ፡ ሰንበት፡ ወለጸሐፊሁኒ፡ ኃጥእ፡ ወአባሲ፡
                      ገብረ፡ ማርያም፡ ሰመሻ፨

                  </ab>
                  </div>
